sketch.compiler.ast.core

Class Function

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FENode
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.Function

  • public class Function
extends FENode
    A function definition. This contains the name, return type, parameter list, and body of a function. Generators, harnesses, models and uninterpreted functions are special kinds of functions with special properties (see Sketch language documentation).
    Author:
    gatoatigrado (nicholas tung) [email: ntung at ntung]
